# Frontend Color Reference - Detailed Brief

## üé® Brand Colors (Social Garden)

### Primary Brand Colors
- **SG Dark**: `#0e2e33` (also `#0E0F0F` / `0 0% 6%` in HSL)
  - Used for: Primary buttons, headings, dark backgrounds, sidebar
  - Hex: `#0e2e33` or `#0E0F0F`
  - HSL: `0 0% 6%`

- **SG Green**: `#20e28f` (also `159 75% 51%` in HSL)
  - Used for: Accent color, buttons (dark mode), success states, highlights
  - Hex: `#20e28f`
  - HSL: `159 75% 51%`
  - Alternative: `#1CBF79`, `#15a366`, `#10a35a` (darker variants)

---

## üåì Light Mode Colors

### Background Colors
- **Main Background**: `#ffffff` (White)
  - Variable: `--background: 0 0% 100%`
  - Usage: Body, main content areas

- **Card Background**: `#ffffff` (White)
  - Variable: `--card: 0 0% 100%`
  - Usage: Cards, modals, dialogs

- **Secondary Background**: `#f5f5f5` (Very light gray - 96%)
  - Variable: `--secondary: 0 0% 96%`
  - Usage: Secondary buttons, subtle backgrounds

- **Muted Background**: `#f5f5f5` (Very light gray - 96%)
  - Variable: `--muted: 0 0% 96%`
  - Usage: Disabled states, subtle UI elements

### Text Colors
- **Primary Text**: `#1a1a1a` (Very dark gray - 10%)
  - Variable: `--foreground: 0 0% 10%`
  - Usage: Body text, primary content

- **Card Text**: `#1a1a1a` (Very dark gray - 10%)
  - Variable: `--card-foreground: 0 0% 10%`
  - Usage: Text on cards

- **Muted Text**: `#737373` (Medium gray - 45%)
  - Variable: `--muted-foreground: 0 0% 45%`
  - Usage: Secondary text, labels, placeholders

- **Secondary Text**: `#1a1a1a` (Very dark gray - 10%)
  - Variable: `--secondary-foreground: 0 0% 10%`
  - Usage: Text on secondary backgrounds

### Border Colors
- **Default Border**: `#e5e5e5` (Light gray - 90%)
  - Variable: `--border: 0 0% 90%`
  - Usage: Borders, dividers

- **Input Border**: `#e5e5e5` (Light gray - 90%)
  - Variable: `--input: 0 0% 90%`
  - Usage: Input fields, form elements

### Button Colors (Light Mode)
- **Primary Button**: 
  - Background: `#0e2e33` (SG Dark)
  - Text: `#ffffff` (White)
  - Hover: Darker shade (90% opacity)

- **Secondary Button**:
  - Background: `#f5f5f5` (Very light gray)
  - Text: `#1a1a1a` (Dark gray)
  - Hover: 80% opacity

- **Destructive Button**:
  - Background: `#ef4444` (Red - 84.2% lightness)
  - Text: `#fafafa` (Very light gray - 98%)
  - Hover: Darker shade (90% opacity)

- **Outline Button**:
  - Border: `#e5e5e5` (Light gray)
  - Background: `#ffffff` (White)
  - Hover: Accent background with accent text

- **Ghost Button**:
  - Background: Transparent
  - Hover: Accent background with accent text

### Accent Colors (Light Mode)
- **Accent**: `#20e28f` (SG Green)
  - Variable: `--accent: var(--sg-green)`
  - Usage: Hover states, focus rings, highlights

- **Accent Foreground**: `#0e2e33` (SG Dark)
  - Variable: `--accent-foreground: var(--sg-dark)`
  - Usage: Text on accent backgrounds

- **Focus Ring**: `#20e28f` (SG Green)
  - Variable: `--ring: var(--sg-green)`
  - Usage: Focus indicators on interactive elements

---

## üåë Dark Mode Colors

### Background Colors
- **Main Background**: `#000000` (Pure Black)
  - Variable: `--background: 0 0% 0%`
  - Usage: Body, main content areas

- **Card Background**: `#0a0a0a` (Very dark gray - 4%)
  - Variable: `--card: 0 0% 4%`
  - Usage: Cards, modals, dialogs

- **Secondary Background**: `#1a1a1a` (Dark gray - 10%)
  - Variable: `--secondary: 0 0% 10%`
  - Usage: Secondary buttons, subtle backgrounds

- **Muted Background**: `#1a1a1a` (Dark gray - 10%)
  - Variable: `--muted: 0 0% 10%`
  - Usage: Disabled states, subtle UI elements

- **Accent Background**: `#262626` (Darker gray - 15%)
  - Variable: `--accent: 0 0% 15%`
  - Usage: Hover states, subtle highlights

### Text Colors
- **Primary Text**: `#fafafa` (Very light gray - 98%)
  - Variable: `--foreground: 0 0% 98%`
  - Usage: Body text, primary content

- **Card Text**: `#fafafa` (Very light gray - 98%)
  - Variable: `--card-foreground: 0 0% 98%`
  - Usage: Text on cards

- **Muted Text**: `#999999` (Medium gray - 60%)
  - Variable: `--muted-foreground: 0 0% 60%`
  - Usage: Secondary text, labels, placeholders

- **Secondary Text**: `#fafafa` (Very light gray - 98%)
  - Variable: `--secondary-foreground: 0 0% 98%`
  - Usage: Text on secondary backgrounds

### Border Colors
- **Default Border**: `#262626` (Dark gray - 15%)
  - Variable: `--border: 0 0% 15%`
  - Usage: Borders, dividers

- **Input Border**: `#262626` (Dark gray - 15%)
  - Variable: `--input: 0 0% 15%`
  - Usage: Input fields, form elements

### Button Colors (Dark Mode)
- **Primary Button**: 
  - Background: `#20e28f` (SG Green)
  - Text: `#000000` (Black)
  - Hover: Darker shade (90% opacity)

- **Secondary Button**:
  - Background: `#1a1a1a` (Dark gray)
  - Text: `#fafafa` (Very light gray)
  - Hover: 80% opacity

- **Destructive Button**:
  - Background: `#991b1b` (Dark red - 30.6% lightness)
  - Text: `#fafafa` (Very light gray - 98%)
  - Hover: Darker shade (90% opacity)

### Accent Colors (Dark Mode)
- **Focus Ring**: `#20e28f` (SG Green)
  - Variable: `--ring: var(--sg-green)`
  - Usage: Focus indicators on interactive elements

